{"id":47,"title":"问：Go语言中的数组和切片有什么区别？","slug":"问：Go语言中的数组和切片有什么区别？-1766595048","excerpt":"","content":"**参考回答：**数组和切片是Go中两种不同类型的数据结构。**数组**长度固定，属于值类型，赋值或函数传参时会拷贝整个数组；**切片**长度可动态变化，属于引用类型，底层引用一个数组，多个切片间可共享底层数据。数组在声明时就分配固定内存，长度是类型组成部分，而切片则是一种对底层数组的抽象，包含指针、长度len和容量cap三个属性。一般在Go编程中更多使用切片，因为其大小灵活可变，而数组多用于底层实现或需要固定长度的场景。\n\n","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"PUBLIC","status":"PUBLISHED","published_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:48.266389+08:00","last_edited_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:48.266389+08:00","notion_page_id":"1f95d23c-2eec-8059-8657-cdf3e3e034f2","notion_last_edit":"2025-05-20T05:56:00Z","author_id":1,"author":{"id":1,"username":"admin","email":"admin@example.com","role":"ADMIN","is_verified":true,"is_active":true,"avatar":"","bio":"","last_login_at":"2025-12-20T00:47:21.462367+08:00","email_verified_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:23.810219+08:00","created_at":"2025-12-19T09:00:38.872854652Z","updated_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:24.010602+08:00","is_admin":true},"stats":{"id":47,"blog_post_id":47,"blog_post":{"id":0,"title":"","slug":"","excerpt":"","content":"","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"","status":"","author_id":0,"author":{"id":0,"username":"","email":"","role":"","is_verified":false,"is_active":false,"avatar":"","bio":"","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","is_admin":false},"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},"view_count":0,"like_count":0,"share_count":0,"comment_count":0,"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.603689+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.603689+08:00"},"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:48.266389+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:48.266389+08:00"}